g.text: Day 1

According to the legend Agamemnon is bragging about how he is a better hunter than the Goddess Artemis which makes the Goddess angry at him. Upon their arrival on Aulis the Goddess will not give them wind for their travel which causes the Archaeans to be stranded on the island. If the Archaeans want to leave the island and head out for Troy, Agamemnon have to sacrifice his daughter Iphigenia.
